prodNameC: 瑞達篩檢諾羅病毒檢測試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
1.Microwell plate：coated with antibodies against Noroviruses.
2.Diluent：protein-buffered NaCl solution
3.wash buffer：phosphate-buffered NaCl solution (10-fold concertrate) contain 0.1% Thimerosal
4.Positive control：Recombinant Norovirus antigens
5.Conjugate：Peroxidase conjugated antibodies against Norovirus in stabilised protein solution
6.Substrate：Urea peroxide/TMB
7.Stop reagent：1 N sulphuric acid

efficacy: 用酵素作為定量分析以確認糞便檢體中諾瓦克病毒基因群 1 及 2 的存在量。
